## Automation Integration

```yaml
# .github/workflows/visual-review.yml
- name: Claude Visual Review
  run: |
    npx playwright test --update-snapshots=missing
    claude --print "Review visual changes in .visual/current vs .visual/baseline.
    Output JSON: {pass: bool, issues: [{severity, description, location}]}"
```
